longBusinessSummary: dMY Squared Technology Group, Inc. does not have significant operations. The company focuses on effecting a merger, capital stock exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. It intends to identify and evaluate businesses in the professional service industry that provide accounting, legal, financial, advisory, and other services to public companies or private companies that are in the process of becoming public companies. The company was incorporated in 2022 and is based in Las Vegas, Nevada.
